<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<bento xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
	<head>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="css/exercises.css" type="text/css" />
		<style type="text/css">
		<![CDATA[
			#questionList p {
				paragraph-start-indent: 30;
				tab-stops: 220;
				color: #0000AA;
				padding-bottom: 20px;
			}
			
			#questionList p a {
				color: #3A00FF;
				font-weight: bold;
			}
		]]>
		</style>
		<script id="model" type="application/xml">
			<settings>
				<param name="delayedMarking" value="true" />
				
				<feedback>
					<feedback min="100%" source="sbf100" />
					<feedback min="60%" source="sbf60-99" />
					<feedback min="40%" source="sbf40-59" />
					<feedback min="20%" source="sbf20-39" />
					<feedback source="sbf0-19" />
				</feedback>
			</settings>
			
			<questions>
				<MultipleChoiceQuestion block="q1Block">
					<answer correct="true" source="q1True">
						<feedback source="gapFillFeedback1" />
					</answer>
					<answer correct="false" source="q1False" />
				</MultipleChoiceQuestion>
			
				<MultipleChoiceQuestion block="q2Block">
					<answer correct="true" source="q2True" />
					<answer correct="false" source="q2False" />
				</MultipleChoiceQuestion>
				
				<MultipleChoiceQuestion block="q3Block">
					<answer correct="true" source="q3True" />
					<answer correct="false" source="q3False" />
				</MultipleChoiceQuestion>
				
				<MultipleChoiceQuestion block="q4Block">
					<answer correct="true" source="q4True" />
					<answer correct="false" source="q4False" />
				</MultipleChoiceQuestion>
				
				<MultipleChoiceQuestion block="q5Block">
					<answer correct="true" source="q5True" />
					<answer correct="false" source="q5False" />
				</MultipleChoiceQuestion>
				
				<MultipleChoiceQuestion block="q6Block">
					<answer correct="true" source="q6True" />
					<answer correct="false" source="q6False" />
				</MultipleChoiceQuestion>
				
				<MultipleChoiceQuestion block="q7Block">
					<answer correct="true" source="q7True" />
					<answer correct="false" source="q7False" />
				</MultipleChoiceQuestion>
				
				<MultipleChoiceQuestion block="q8Block">
					<answer correct="true" source="q8True" />
					<answer correct="false" source="q8False" />
				</MultipleChoiceQuestion>
				
				<MultipleChoiceQuestion block="q9Block">
					<answer correct="true" source="q9True" />
					<answer correct="false" source="q9False" />
				</MultipleChoiceQuestion>
			</questions>
		</script>
	</head>
	
	<body>
		<header>
			Now decide whether the sentences are true or false.  Do the quiz.  Look at the simple present in the questions and answers.
		</header>
		
		<section id="body">
			<img class="rightFloat" src="media/tiger.png" />
			
			<ol id="questionList">
				<li id="q1Block">
					Tigers teach their babies to swim.
					<p><a id="q1True">True</a><tab/><a id="q1False">False</a></p>
				</li>
				
				<li id="q2Block">
					Some mice have 10 babies every month.
					<p><a id="q2True">True</a><tab/><a id="q2False">False</a></p>
				</li>
				
				<li id="q3Block">
					The lion only lives in Africa.
					<p><a id="q3True">True</a><tab/><a id="q3False">False</a></p>
				</li>
				
				<li id="q4Block">
					The kangaroo carries its babies in its pocket.
					<p><a id="q4True">True</a><tab/><a id="q4False">False</a></p>
				</li>
				
				<li id="q5Block">
					Some birds fly 14,000 miles every year.
					<p><a id="q5True">True</a><tab/><a id="q5False">False</a></p>
				</li>
				
				<li id="q6Block">
					A dog called Toby has $15m dollars in the bank.
					<p><a id="q6True">True</a><tab/><a id="q6False">False</a></p>
				</li>
				
				<li id="q7Block">
					A baby African elephant weighs 4,000kg.
					<p><a id="q7True">True</a><tab/><a id="q7False">False</a></p>
				</li>
				
				<li id="q8Block">
					Some birds sleep while they fly.
					<p><a id="q8True">True</a><tab/><a id="q8False">False</a></p>
				</li>
				
				<li id="q9Block">
					Americans spend $100m on food for dogs and cats every year.
					<p><a id="q9True">True</a><tab/><a id="q9False">False</a></p>
				</li>
			</ol>
		</section>
		
		<section id="gapFillFeedback1">
			This is the feedback for gapfill 1.  It is supposed to test out substitution of
			values.<br/><br/>
			<p>Your answer: {{=yourAnswer}}</p>
			<p>Correct answer: {{=correctAnswer}}</p>
		</section>
		
		<section id="sbf100">100%</section>
		<section id="sbf60-99">60% - 99%</section>
		<section id="sbf40-59">40% - 59%</section>
		<section id="sbf20-39">20% - 39%</section>
		<section id="sbf0-19">Unmatched (i.e. 0% - 19%)</section>
		
	</body>
	
</bento>